<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Wazokonstriktor damjalary &yacute;a-da burun
spre&yacute;leri.&nbsp;&Ccedil;i&#351;megi a&yacute;yr&yacute;arlar we
&yacute;okarky howa &yacute;ollaryny&#328; patentini
&yacute;okarlandyr&yacute;arlar.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de bolsa, olary 5-7
g&uuml;nden k&ouml;p ulanyp bolma&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Be&yacute;leki bejeri&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri bilen bilelikde bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Intranazal gl&yacute;ukokortikosteroidler.&nbsp;Bular gormonal
dermanlar, &ccedil;i&#351;megi we &ccedil;i&#351;megi azald&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>ENT
organlaryny&#328; birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n keselleri bolan n&auml;saglarda
ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&ccedil;erki enjamlar:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>a&#351;aky e&#328;egi&#328; gi&#328;elmegine k&ouml;mek
ed&yacute;&auml;n enjamlar &yacute;e&#328;il obstruktiw uky apnoe sindromly
n&auml;saglar &uuml;&ccedil;in bellenilip bilner;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Dili&#328; &ccedil;&ouml;kmegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
al&yacute;an dala&#351;g&auml;rler di&#351; &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi bolan
n&auml;saglara, temporomandibul&yacute;ar boguny&#328; patologi&yacute;asy,
agzy&#328; a&ccedil;ylanda &ccedil;&auml;klendirilmegi bellenilip bilner;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Yzygiderli poloositiveitel howa &yacute;oly basy&#351;y (CPAP)
bejergisi, &ccedil;e&yacute;e turba arkaly burun maskasyna howa
iber&yacute;&auml;n enjamy&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen dem al&yacute;an
howany&#328; polo positiveitel basy&#351;yny d&ouml;retmekden ybaratdyr,
&#351;e&yacute;lelik bilen &yacute;okarky howa &yacute;oluny&#328;
&ccedil;&ouml;kmegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni alar, &ouml;&yacute;keni&#328;
geli&#351; mukdaryny we kislorod bilen do&yacute;gunlygyny
&yacute;okarlandyrar. gowula&#351;&yacute;ar;&nbsp;CPAP bejergisi
sindromy&#328; orta we agyr derejeleri &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar,
hepdede azyndan 5 gije azyndan 3-4 sagat ulanylsa t&auml;sirli bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki
amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>ENT organlaryny&#328;
patologi&yacute;asy &uuml;&ccedil;in hirurgiki interwensi&yacute;a
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;E&#328;egi&#328; bozulmagy &uuml;&ccedil;in,
i&ccedil;erki enjamlar &yacute;a-da CPAP bejergisi &#351;owsuz bolsa, hirurgiki
bejergisi g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&#328; &yacute;a&yacute;ran
ENT operasi&yacute;alary:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>burun septumyny&#328; egriligi bilen septoplastika;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>tonzillektomi&yacute;a &yacute;a-da adenoidektomi&yacute;a -
ulaldylan tonzalar bilen;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>uvulopalatofaryngoplastika - agzdaky artykma&ccedil;
&yacute;um&#351;ak dokumalary a&yacute;yrmak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&uuml;ndiz uky.&nbsp;Bejerilmedik uky apnoesi bolan
n&auml;saglarda &yacute;ol hadysalaryny&#328; d&ouml;remek howpy sagdyn adamlara
garany&#328;da 6-7 esse &yacute;okarydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Card&uuml;rek-damar keselleri (arterial gipertoni&yacute;a,
dowamly &yacute;&uuml;rek &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi, miokard infarkty).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Erektil disfunksi&yacute;a.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&ouml;z keselleri.&nbsp;I&#328; so&#328;ky g&ouml;zleglere
g&ouml;r&auml;, uky apnoe sindromy bilen glaukomany&#328;
&ouml;s&uuml;&#351;ini&#328; arasyndaky baglany&#351;yk subut edildi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Partn&yacute;orda ukusyzlyk.&nbsp;Horlamak uky bilen
p&auml;sgel&ccedil;ilik d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;r, bu ma&#351;gala
durmu&#351;yna &yacute;aramaz t&auml;sir edip biler we hatda depressi&yacute;a
seb&auml;p bolup biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ccedil;agalarda burun dem al&#351;yna &ouml;z wagtynda baha
bermek we g&ouml;rkezmelere g&ouml;r&auml; adenoidleri a&yacute;yrmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;agalarda malokl&yacute;uzi&yacute;any wagtynda bejermek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>i&#328; amatly agramy saklamak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;ilim &ccedil;ekmekden we spirtli i&ccedil;gileri
azaltmakdan saklanmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>di&#328;e psihiatry&#328; g&ouml;rkezmesi bo&yacute;un&ccedil;a
antidepressant bejergisi;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>durnukly uky g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ini go&#351;mak bilen &quot;arassa&ccedil;ylyk&quot;
ukusyny saklamak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Islendik &yacute;a&#351;da dowamly keselleri&#328; we
t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik faktorlaryny&#328; barlygynda yzygiderli
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351; synaglary, 40 &yacute;a&#351;dan h&ouml;kmany
&yacute;yllyk lukman&ccedil;ylyk barlagy;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>uky wagtynda dem aly&#351; bozulmalaryny ir &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykarmak we wagtynda lukman&ccedil;ylyk k&ouml;megi g&ouml;zlemek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Wagtynda
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarmak we dogry bejermek bilen doly bejermek,
horlanmagy we g&uuml;ndiz ukusyny &yacute;ok etmek m&uuml;mkin.&nbsp;CPAP
bejergisi bilen 4-8 hepdede gowula&#351;ma bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bejerilmedik obstruktiw
gije apnoe sindromy &yacute;&uuml;rek-damar keseli we &yacute;adawlyk
hadysalary seb&auml;pli keseli&#328; we &ouml;l&uuml;mi&#328; 3-5 esse
&yacute;okarlanmagyna getir&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Her hili horlanmak obstruktiw uky apnoe sindromyny&#328;
alamatymy?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Artykma&ccedil; agram bu kesele n&auml;hili t&auml;sir
ed&yacute;&auml;r?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Dowamly &yacute;agda&yacute;larym obstruktiw uky apnasyna
n&auml;hili t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;r?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ol &yacute;erde ha&yacute;sy bejergiler bar?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygy&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni n&auml;dip
